snippet.title: NON DRAMA: Real True Crime -   Case Updates
snippet.description:
Case Updates: Heidi Planck, Cleo Smith, Glenda Parton, Summer Wells, Daniel Robinson

Anyone in my videos is innocent until proven guilty
Rules: 1. be respectful to host, mods and chat 2.do not talk about other creators/channels 3.behave like adults 4. don't be a dick!

Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCn-EXLEpy2Sx-yMQbpZmWiA/join

Please join our community, and help spread these stories
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/NZMysteries/
Website: https://newzealandmissing.wordpress.com/
Podcast: https://anchor.fm/newzealandmysteries
Email: nzmissing@gmail.com

If you are able to support the channel to get better equipment and continue the fight for these victims and their families you can buy me a coffee!
go to: https://www.buymeacoffee.com/nzmysteries
or Paypal: https://www.paypal.com/donate?hosted_button_id=NK5VDGRYE6ESY
NZM 38-9010-0626032-04

Sources/links

Glenda Parton:  https://www.newson6.com/story/6196dffa7e7abe0c12cf0a63/search-continues-for-2-missing-people-from-turley?__vfz=medium%3Dstandalone_top_pages
Summer Wells;  https://www.wjhl.com/news/local/summer-wells-tn/large-scale-search-for-summer-wells-enters-day-2-as-crews-return-to-beech-creek/
Daniel Robinson:  https://www.newsnationnow.com/us-news/southwest/father-hoping-new-details-help-find-missing-daniel-robinson/
